<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>frontend</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="main.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="logo" href="#">YSR BANK</a>
            
            <img id="mobile-cta" class="mobile-menu" src="menu.svg" alt="open navigation">

            <nav>
                <img id="mobile-exit" class="mobile-menu-exit" src="menu.svg" alt="close navigation">
                <ul class="primary-nav">
                    <li class="current"><a href="/">Home page</a></li>
                    <li><a href="Accounts.ejs">Accounts</a></li>
                    <li><a href="payment.ejs">payment</a></li>
                    <li><a href="History.ejs">History</a></li>
                    
                </ul>

                <ul class="secondary-nav">
                    <li><a href="Help.ejs">Help</a></li>
                    <li><a href="Notifications.ejs">Notifications</a></li>
                    
                </ul>
                
            </nav>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="main">
            <h1>welcome to YSR BANK</h1>
            <img src="building.jpg" alt="building">
            <p>YSR Bank, India's International Bank Offers Internet Banking Services, Mobile Banking 
                Services, Accounts, Loans, Financial Services to Corporates. 
                In this bank we provide low interest personal loan,home loan and educational loan.
                we assure you that we give atmost priorty to keep your information confidantial.
            </p>
            <h2>warning</h2>
            <p>Bank never asks any information regrading bank account details
               for any purpose. The Reserve Bank has appealed to members of public 
               not to respond to such mails and not to share their bank account details
               with anyone for any purpose. from customers. Fake addresses and phone numbers
               of Bank's branches are created by miscreants on google search.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script>

        const mobileBtn = document.getElementById('mobile-cta')
            nav = document.querySelector('nav')
            mobileBtnExit = document.getElementById('mobile-exit');

        mobileBtn.addEventListener('click', () =>{
            nav.classList.add('menu-btn');
        })

        mobileBtnExit.addEventListener('click', () =>{
            nav.classList.remove('menu-btn');
        })
    </script>
</body>
</html>